title: DAZ3D - Poser - Dead Walker - Mr Happy HD (DAZ 20184) DIM
description:
Two, Two, Two fears in One! Whether it is the Zombie apocalypse that worries your soul, or simply the make-up wearing makers of balloon animals who fill your nightmares with dread, Mr Happy can fulfill your horror on both sides.

As an undead Walker in the zombie wastelands, these textures are truly terrifying, but this set also comes with a version for a deeper horror as the clown makeup gets applied and happy childhood visions get corrupted into something sinister.

This masterfully crafted character comes complete with standard Low density morphs, and a set of custom crafted High Definition morphs, bringing a new level of realism to the character
